_sText:
Im not the brains behind this map but I am a big promoter of things that are good in life and this map is Awsome!!!!!!! honestly one of the best custom maps that I have played.  I thought it was creative having the players fight on skyscrapers with the ability to go into and out of the buildings too.  It has 2 bomb sites and runs very nicely. It is definatley worth the download. You will enjoy this on your servers map rotation too.  Enough of me let the map speak for it's self................ENJOY


feedback is welcome please make coments about the map!
